首頁




		急診醫學部










Missions
 1) Cultivate future leaders and foster advanced research in the Emergency Medicine 2) Provide state-of-the-art care to those with acute illness  3) Reform the health care system in Taiwan本部使命一.領導台灣的急診醫學研究發展，培育急診醫學領導人才二.世界一流的急重症病人服務三.籌劃建立健全的國家醫療衛生體系  ​ 




